text: Mr. Malcom Coppenny gave an outstanding service on my fight to and from Philipines. He was very patient and quite resourceful in obtaining alternative to acquiring means to get the right flight and price.He is a person one can rely on receiving the best for busy people traveling.Thanks again for the excellent service rendered by Mr. Coppeny.
